output/

This folder stores the results generated by your program after processing the images.

output/
├── results/
└── processed_images/

1.results/

This folder contains the final inspection results. You can save the processed images or a text file with inspection outcomes.

Example:

results/
├── inspection_result1.png
├── inspection_result2.png
├── inspection_result3.png
└── report.txt

Example report.txt
AUTOMATED QUALITY INSPECTION REPORT

--------------------------------------
Image Name          Status
--------------------------------------
test1.jpg           PASS
test2.jpg           FAIL
test3.jpg           PASS
test4.jpg           FAIL
--------------------------------------

Inspection Completed Successfully.

2.processed_images/

This folder stores the intermediate images produced during preprocessing.

Example:

processed_images/
├── grayscale.png
├── blurred.png
├── threshold.png
└── contours.png

These images are useful for debugging and demonstrating each stage of the computer vision pipeline.
